         </p>
         <p>
          I feel pretty steady and haul my laptop all over creation. Every once in a while I will teeter to the left just a little (I injured my right)‚Ä¶ But it seems like a cane would just be another thing to carry‚Ä¶ As 90% of the time I feel steady.
